00:00:06.060 --> 00:00:08.620
-Good afternoon everyone,
and welcome to the Radcliffe

00:00:08.620 --> 00:00:10.630
Institute for Advanced Study.

00:00:10.630 --> 00:00:11.450
I'm Liz Cohen.

00:00:11.450 --> 00:00:13.420
