the Institute, and I

00:00:13.420 --> 00:00:16.840
am delighted to welcome
you to Radcliffe,

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:20.190
an institution powered
by the same commitment

00:00:20.190 --> 00:00:24.620
to ideas and discovery
that HUBweek celebrates.

00:00:24.620 --> 00:00:29.690
HUBweek, a civic collaboration
between the Boston Globe, MIT,

00:00:29.690 --> 00:00:32.400
Mass General
