that transcends disciplines

00:00:48.570 --> 00:00:52.850
and sharing that work
with the public, with you.

00:00:52.850 --> 00:00:57.040
In addition to serving as
dean of this institute,

00:00:57.040 --> 00:01:00.610
I wear a second hat as
a professor of history

00:01:00.610 --> 00:01:03.080
