00:04:22.550 --> 00:04:23.870
and their organizations.

00:04:23.870 --> 00:04:27.630
It will be moderated
by Ross Douthat, who's

00:04:27.630 --> 00:04:29.806
a columnist at the
New York Times.

00:04:29.806 --> 00:04:33.180
Our third program we
call academic ventures,

00:04:33.180 --> 00:04:36.220
