00:04:51.190 --> 00:04:52.870
international refugee crisis.

00:04:52.870 --> 00:04:55.520
And I think you have a card
for that, the yellow card,

00:04:55.520 --> 00:04:56.980
on your seat.

00:04:56.980 --> 00:04:59.620
Our annual full day
science symposium

00:04:59.620 --> 00:05:02.160
will take place on
